import {
  FormControl,
  FormControlLabel,
  FormHelperText,
  InputLabel,
  TextField,
} from "@material-ui/core"

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="xs">
      <form>
        <TextField
          variant="outlined"
          margin="normal"
          required
          fullWidth
          id="email"
          label="Email Address"
          name="email"
          autoComplete="email"
          autoFocus
        ></TextField>
      </form>
      <FormControl>
        <InputLabel htmlFor="email">Email Address</InputLabel>
        <input id="email" aria-describedby="email-helper-text"></input>
        <FormHelperText id="email-helper-text">
          Please enter your email.
        </FormHelperText>
      </FormControl>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Login
